The Information Security Institute at The Johns Hopkins University (JHUISI) is
planning for substantial multi-year growth in the area of Information Security
and Cryptography. Our administration is committed at the highest level to
substantially growing our security program with multiple, concurrent tenure-
track offers expected this year, at all levels. We particularly encourage
candidates with research interests in Cryptography, Systems and Network
Security, Cloud and Mobile Security, and Health-Related Applications Security.
